      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is sound with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received regular oil changes. The exterior is clean but does show some minor road wear, including a few small stone chips on the hood and light scratches near the door handles. Inside, the cabin is tidy and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the upholstery consistent with its age. Overall, this is a dependable car that offers a great balance of performance and value.",
