    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s sparkling inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 48500.0,
