    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of Bavarian engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains the centerpiece, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing that delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen retains its factory-spec Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, offering crisp, mechanical shift gates. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with the rear subframe mounting points inspected and reinforced to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Performance is sharpened by the Variable M Differential Lock and original-spec ventilated compound rotors. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a factory-fresh cabin, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
